# 🧠 4. Core Idea (Important for Interview)

👉 System built on:

* Microservices
* Event-driven architecture
* AI integration
* Role-based flows

👉 Goal:
**Reduce hiring friction + improve candidate quality**

---

# 🏗️ 5. System Architecture

```text
Frontend (Next.js)
        ↓
Auth Layer (JWT + Middleware)
        ↓
-------------------------------------
| Auth | User | Job | Payment       |
-------------------------------------
        ↓
Kafka (Event Streaming)
        ↓
Utils Service (Mail + AI)
        ↓
-------------------------------------
| PostgreSQL | Redis | Cloudinary  |
-------------------------------------
```

---

# 🔄 6. Application Flow

## 🧑 Job Seeker Flow

```text
Register/Login
   ↓
Complete Profile
   ↓
Create/Upload Resume
   ↓
Resume Analyzer + ATS Score
   ↓
Browse Jobs
   ↓
Apply for Jobs
   ↓
Track Applications
   ↓
Get Notifications
```

---

## 🧑‍💼 Recruiter Flow

```text
Register/Login
   ↓
Create Company Profile
   ↓
Post Job
   ↓
Receive Applications
   ↓
View Resume + Score
   ↓
Shortlist Candidates
```

